# ğŸ› ï¸ Development

Clone the repo and install in editable mode:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/eivl/archivus.git
cd archivus
pip install -e .[dev]
```
Run locally from source:
```bash
python -m archivus sync --to ~/Games/WoW/_retail_
```

